<div xmlns:perseus="http://www.perseus.org/meta/perseus.rdfs#" xmlns:dctype="http://purl.org/dc/dcmitype/" xmlns:tufts="http://www.tufts.edu/" xmlns:alph="http://alpheios.net/namespaces/tei" class="alpheios-lex-text_container en">
    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n1867" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">βλάπτω, βλάβω</span></b> , aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἔβλαψα, βλάψα</span>, pass. pres. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">βλάβεται</span>, perf. part. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">βεβλαμμένος</span>, aor. 1, 3 pl., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐβλάφθησαν</span>, part. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">βλαφθείς</span>, aor. 2 <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐβλάβην</span>,
          3 pl. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἔβλαβεν, βλάβεν</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">impede,
            arrest;</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τόν γε θεοὶ βλάπτουσι κελεύθου</span>, <i><span class="en">Od. 1.195</span></i>; (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἵππω</span>) <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ὄζῳ ἐνὶ βλαφθέντε</span>,
          ‘caught’ in, <i><span class="en">Il. 6.39</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Il. 15.647</span></i>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">; βλάψε δέ οἱ φίλα γούνατα</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 7.271</span></i>; so pass., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">βλάβεται γούνατα</span>, ‘totter,’ <i><span class="en">Od.
            13.34</span></i>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">; βεβλαμμένον: ἦτορ</span>, ‘arrested in
          life's flow,’ i. e. ‘wounded in the heart,’ <i><span class="en">Il. 16.660</span></i>; metaph., <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">harm</span> the mind.,
            <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">infatuate;</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τὸν δέ τις ἀ̄θανάτων βλἁψε φρένας</span>,
            <i><span class="en">Od. 14.178</span></i>; and without <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">φρένας</span>, (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">-Ἄτη</span>) <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">βλάπτουσ᾽ ἀνθρώπους</span>,
            <i><span class="en">Il. 9.507</span></i>; pass., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">βλαφθείς</span>, <i><span class="en">Il.
            9.512</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
